description: [``botocore``] Include params set in provide-client-param event handlers in dynamic context params for endpoint resolution.
[``botocore``] This release updates GetMetricDataV2 API, to support metric data up-to last 35 days

[``botocore``] Added support to modify the cluster mode configuration for the existing ElastiCache ReplicationGroups. Customers can now modify the configuration from cluster mode disabled to cluster mode enabled.
[``botocore``] This release fixes DescribePackages API error with null filter value parameter.
[``botocore``] Add methods for inspecting and debugging stages: ListStageSessions, GetStageSession, ListParticipants, GetParticipant, and ListParticipantEvents.

[``botocore``] This release provides support for Ready2Run and GPU workflows, an improved read set filter, the direct upload of read sets into Omics Storage, and annotation parsing for analytics stores.
[``botocore``] This release fixes DescribePackages API error with null filter value parameter.
[``botocore``] Update FIPS endpoints for GovCloud (US) regions in SDK.
[``botocore``] This release adds 2 new Support APIs, DescribeCreateCaseOptions and DescribeSupportedLanguages. You can use these new APIs to get available support languages.
